skills.description:
Once every 20s, while this ship's HP is above 60.0%: spawns a shield around this ship (lasts 8s, can negate 1.0% (4.0%) total DMG);
if there are other ships afloat in your Vanguard: doubles the amount of DMG this shield can negate, and this ship tanks 50.0% of the DMG your other 
Vanguard ships take for 8s. While this ship's HP is below 60.0%: the above effect will not activate; instead, this ship's TRP increases by 5.0% (15.0%).
